  "text": "Having established that a desire for integration within electronic gatherings is often strong, I have identified three mechanisms that help generate and sustain high levels of collective activity: (a) celebrating rituals, (b) engaging in gift exchange, and (c) building what Durkheimian scholars [CITATION_1] call \"communities of memory.\"",
